data.description: Discover this exquisite 3/2 Ranch style home with Bonus Room that offers a perfect blend of comfort and elegance. Step inside and be greeted by a spacious open concept floor plan, featuring a separate formal dining room and a large family room adorned with a charming brick wood-burning fireplace. With LP Vinyl Flooring throughout the main level, this home exudes both style and practicality. The generously sized Owners Suite boasts a trayed ceiling, providing an air of sophistication. Indulge in the on-suite bath, complete with a separate garden tub and double sinks for added convenience. But wait, it doesn't stop there - With two additional well-proportioned bedrooms, there is ample space for everyone to unwind and relax. Plus, an added bonus room and enclosed sunroom provide versatile areas for work or play. Step outside into the fully fenced backyard, creating an ideal oasis for relaxation or entertaining guests. Plus, with a 2-car garage, your vehicles will always have a place to call home. ****SELLER willing to help BUYER with a negotiated closing cost amount at closing *****
